               <p>
                  <hi rend="italic">Prisoner.</hi> I have been a cripple in my left hand twenty years, and they took a description of me. <hi rend="italic">Witness.</hi> You showed me your left hand on the last occasion in the cell at Worship-street—I have no doubt of you, and have witnesses here who were here on the last occasion.</p>
